    "dict": [
        {
            "type": "name",
            "source": "🐱 Phycat theme Info & Help",
            "target": "🐱 Phycat 主題資訊與說明"
        },
        {
            "type": "markdown",
            "source": "true",
            "target": "true"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "### Phycat Theme \\n A vibrant, glassmorphism aesthetic theme for Obsidian. \\n\\n [Github Repository](https://github.com/sumruler/obsidian-theme-phycat) | [Report Issue](https://github.com/sumruler/obsidian-theme-phycat/issues)| [Support](https://www.phycat.cn/donate.html)",
            "target": "### Phycat 主題 \\n 一款充滿活力、帶有玻璃擬態美感的 Obsidian 主題。 \\n\\n [Github 儲存庫](https://github.com/sumruler/obsidian-theme-phycat) | [回報問題](https://github.com/sumruler/obsidian-theme-phycat/issues)| [支持作者](https://www.phycat.cn/donate.html)"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "**💡 Font Recommendation:** \\n This theme is optimized for [**LXGW WenKai**](https://github.com/lxgw/LxgwWenKai). Please install it for the best experience.",
            "target": "**💡 字體建議：** \\n 這個主題已針對 [**LXGW WenKai**](https://github.com/lxgw/LxgwWenKai) 最佳化。建議安裝以獲得最佳體驗。"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "**🪟 Pro Tip: Independent Settings View** \\n Press `Ctrl+P` and search for `Style Settings: Show style settings view`. This opens the settings in a separate pane instead of a modal, preventing it from blocking your view.",
            "target": "**🪟 小技巧：獨立設定檢視** \\n 按下 `Ctrl+P` 並搜尋 `Style Settings: Show style settings view`。這會將設定開在獨立窗格中，而不是彈出視窗，避免遮住目前畫面。"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "**🧩 Plugin Recommendation: Hover Editor** \\n It is highly recommended to install the [**Hover Editor**](https://github.com/nothingislost/obsidian-hover-editor) plugin. You can turn the settings pane mentioned above into a floating window to tweak the theme in real-time.",
            "target": "**🧩 外掛推薦：Hover Editor** \\n 強烈建議安裝 [**Hover Editor**](https://github.com/nothingislost/obsidian-hover-editor) 外掛。你可以把上面提到的設定窗格變成浮動視窗，方便即時微調主題。"
        },
